textBeforeTable: Attributes Defines a supplemental name/value attribute. This can be used to add additional information to elements that are not specifically defined ComplexType Extra - Enumeration Men : Men - Enumeration Women : Women - Enumeration Open : Open - Enumeration Mixed : Mixed SimpleType EventGender - Enumeration Male : Male - Enumeration Female : Female - Enumeration M : Male - deprecated - Enumeration F : Female - deprecated SimpleType PersonGender Used for match race entries and mark rounding sides (at a minimum) or tack - Enumeration Port : "left" in layman terms - Enumeration Starboard : "right" in layman terms SimpleType PortStarboard Format used for the races in a Divison - Enumeration FleetRace : Fleet Racing (what most of sailing is) - Enumeration TeamRace : Team Racing (see RRS Appendix D) - Enumeration MatchRace : Match Racing (see RRS Appendix C) SimpleType DivisionType
textAfterTable: Other Extra name/value information for additional unstructured information Attributes Attribute Type Documentation PersonID xsd:string document-internal identifier for this person IFPersonID xsd:string persistent identifier for the person, usually the ISAF SailorID (see IFSource) FamilyName xsd:string Family (Last) name of the person GivenName xsd:string Given (first, familiar) name of the person NOC IFNationCode Person's country identity Gender PersonGender Person's gender ClassificationGroup IFCfcnGroup Person's classification group (see ISAF Classification Code) ClassificationStatus IFCfcnStatus the status of the person's classification group ClassificationExpiry xsd:date date on which the classification group expires ContactPhone xsd:string contact phone for the person. ContactEmail xsd:string contact email address for the person ComplexType Crew Boat crew (combines person with the CrewPosition enumeration)
